{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: "(Reaches the top of the building) We're finally out... huh?", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'The guards are still after us.', 4: '2'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryLouDianNew.prefab', 3: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Roland', 3: "Nat isn't going to... let me go so easily...", 4: '1'}
{3: '(Roland concentrates the Punishing Virus to his right arm) ...'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: "(Breaks away from Nanami's control) If I can't beat you...", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: '(Dashes toward Roland) ...!', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Roland', 3: '(Jumps backward) I\'ll leave it to "destiny"...', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Roland jumps off from up high, and the golden guards leap toward him like hungry beasts...'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryLouDianNew.prefab', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "(Jumps after Roland) He'll get torn into pieces...", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Nanami was careless...', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "(Battles the guards) Shouldn't have given him the opportunity to act freely.", 4: '2'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryLouDianNew.prefab', 3: '1'}
{1: '1', 3: 'Nanami enters a deadly battle with the guards for Roland...'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Roland', 3: '(Concentrates the Punishing Virus on his arm) All of you... move...!', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Although his frame is severely damaged, Roland still manages to throw off the guards and dashes toward the golden light beam...'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: "(Leaps toward the golden light) I've been watching... If I take advantage of its force, I might be able to thrown out of here...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: 'Even though my body will probably be crushed by the impact...', 4: '1'}

{2: 'Roland', 3: '(The light beam is right ahead) As long as my M.I.N.D. device gets carried far enough from the antigen above the desert... I can still summon enough Corrupted here to drag me away...', 4: '1'}
{3: "A slashing tornado appears behind Roland's back..."}
{3: 'After a wave of slashes, the whole floor begins to collapse... Before Roland can jump into the beam, he is hit by a fallen metal plate and falls into the depths...'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Roland', 3: '(His body keeps getting hit by fallen objects) ...!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryLouDianNew.prefab', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 3: 'Among the debris, Nanami is holding on to a torn cable, hanging above the gulf...'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'That was so, so close...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Roland, wait for me! Nanami's coming to get you.", 4: '1'}
